o brother , where art thou ? is a 2001 american romantic comedy film directed by joel coen and starring joel coen , john turturro , and tim blake nelson . the film was directed by joel coen , and stars jodie coen , john turturro , and tim blake nelson . the film was directed by joel coen and joel coen . the film was nominated for the academy award for best foreign language film , but was not accepted as a nominee .